	title="Funtown Splashtown USA: Tips, Best Rides & How to Plan Your Day"
	description="Maine's largest amusement and water park combo is less than 2 miles from Saco Bay Hotel. A complete guide to Excalibur, the water park, and how to make the most of a full day."
